room_title: Escape room "Once Upon a Time" by Red Door Escape Room Concord in Concord
room_description: Trouble is brewing in the kingdom as treasured magical items have gone missing.  The evidence points to Rumpelstiltskin being the culprit and rumors have circulated that he is trying to enact a curse on all the land.  Brave adventurers are called upon to break into Rumpelstiltskin’s castle and find the missing artifacts and stop him before it’s too late!
